  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Implement and mature a standard, repeatable process to better manage development activities and forecast what needs to&#xD;
    be done. Increase the&amp;nbsp;ability to understand organizational performance in order to tailor, adopt and enact&#xD;
    appropriate processes.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Many studies have shown that organizations with mature processes achieve high predictability.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    For example,&amp;nbsp;one&amp;nbsp;organization&amp;nbsp;reported over 30% reduction of cost and budget overruns after obtaining&#xD;
    SEI Maturity Improvement Level 4.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    See the following reference:&lt;br />&#xD;
    Haley, T., B. Ireland, E. Wojtaszek, D. Nash and R. Dion, &quot;Raytheon Electronic Systems Experience inSoftware Process&#xD;
    Improvement&quot;, SEI Technical Report CMU/SEI-95-TR017, November, 1995.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Symptoms that indicate the need to improve process governance and compliance include the following:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No process standard across organization.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Inconsistent adoption or no adoption.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No criteria to understand how to tailor the process.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No clear roles and job descriptions.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Inability to harvest past experiences to improve the process.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solutions&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following solutions help to improve process governance and compliance:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/architect_and_communicate_soln_4B3FC0DE.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xf5XkLRaEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Architect and Communicate the Solution&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp; - Develop the architecture and&#xD;
        communicate the solution to the team.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/effectively_manage_rqmts_monitor_scope_D8751333.html&quot; guid=&quot;_CEDYULRZEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Effectively Manage Requirements and Monitor Scope&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Manage stakeholders'&#xD;
        expectations and communicate the value of the selected scope.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_lifecycle_collaboration_31E3F561.html&quot; guid=&quot;_R3YuMLRZEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Improve Lifecycle Collaboration&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Improve collaboration by providing&#xD;
        lifecycle integration across otherwise disconnected team members.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
